Package: ollama
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, adduser
Description: Get up and running with large language models locally
 Ollama is a tool for running large language models locally. It bundles
 model weights, configuration and data into a single package, and provides
 a simple CLI and REST API to run and manage models such as Llama, Gemma,
 Qwen and DeepSeek.
